  "text": "Slope Decision Support System One of the key objectives of the EU funded ECOSLOPES project was to provide a Slope Decision Support System (SDSS) to help practitioners to assess their slopes and select appropriate vegetation to help stabilise them. The SDSS may be trialled as a development version (Ecoslopes Manual, in prep.; [CITATION_1] and it is intended that with the benefit of user feedback its scope will be confirmed to provide the necessary guidance for eco-engineering and soil bioengineering applications.",
